claim.claim-text:
A method of processing a stream of video data which comprises a sequence of frames (200), the method comprising:
receiving the stream of video data;
detecting a freeze condition;
when detecting the freeze condition,
creating a three-dimensional environment from a frame (215) of the sequence of frames (200);
generating a series of frames (321-325) from the three-dimensional environment, the series of frames (321-325) representing the three-dimensional environment from a plurality of points of view (511-513); and
inserting the generated series of frames (321-325) into the sequence of frames (200) to generate a modified sequence (300) of frames which conceals a freeze.
